0.01: Initial release
- Created basic grid visualization of year progress
- Added percentage display
- Implemented auto-update every minute
- Added touch controls for exit 

0.02: Optimization update
- Optimized drawing code by using large rectangles instead of individual squares
- Improved performance by reducing the number of drawing operations
- Adjusted square size and spacing for better visual appearance
- Simplified app structure and removed unnecessary code 

0.03: Perfectly fill the screen